---
// src/sections/Contact.astro
---
<section id="contact" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 scroll-reveal">
        <span>تواصل</span> 
        <span class="gradient-text-arabic">معنا</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary mx-auto mb-4 scroll-reveal"></div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg scroll-reveal">
        لديك أسئلة أو استفسارات؟ نحن هنا للمساعدة. تواصل معنا من خلال أي من
        قنوات الاتصال التالية.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 scroll-reveal group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-500 transition-colors duration-300">
            <i class="ri-whatsapp-line text-green-600 text-2xl group-hover:text-white transition-colors"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">واتساب</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">تواصل معنا مباشرة عبر الواتساب للحصول على رد سريع</p>
          <a 
            href="https://wa.me/966506564275" 
            target="_blank"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-green-600 font-medium hover:text-green-700 transition-colors"
          >
            <span dir="ltr">+966 50 656 4275</span>
            <i class="ri-external-link-line"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 scroll-reveal group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors duration-300">
            <i class="ri-mail-line text-blue-600 text-2xl group-hover:text-white transition-colors"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">البريد الإلكتروني</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">أرسل لنا رسالة عبر البريد الإلكتروني</p>
          <a 
            href="mailto:info@wafrli.com" 
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-blue-600 font-medium hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
          >
            <span dir="ltr">info@wafrli.com</span>
            <i class="ri-external-link-line"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 scroll-reveal group">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-orange-500 transition-colors duration-300">
            <i class="ri-map-pin-line text-orange-600 text-2xl group-hover:text-white transition-colors"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">العنوان</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">موقعنا في المملكة العربية السعودية</p>
          <p class="text-orange-600 font-medium">مكة المكرمة</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-12 text-center" hidden>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">تابعنا على</h3>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-6">
          <a
            href="#"
            class="w-14 h-14 aspect-square bg-gradient-to-r from-[#E4405F] to-[#C13584] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <i class="ri-instagram-line text-xl"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            class="w-14 h-14 aspect-square bg-gradient-to-r from-black to-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <i class="ri-twitter-x-line text-xl"></i>
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            class="w-14 h-14 aspect-square bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0077B5] to-[#005885] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
          >
            <i class="ri-linkedin-line text-xl"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 